ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAppointment of THOMAS RANKIN of St. Catharines, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first, in the place of Margo Buchanan, whose term has expired.
